		'¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
		#Region "Methods"

			'¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨
			Friend	Sub RegisterFavourite(ByVal	dataEntry	As SAPFavoriteDTO)

				If Me.ct_FavList.Count	= 0
					dataEntry.SeqNo	= 1
					Me.ct_FavList.Add(1, dataEntry)
					Return
				End If
				'..................................................
				Dim	ln_Indx	= Me.CheckExists(dataEntry)
				'..................................................
				If ln_Indx.Equals(0)	Then	Return
				'..................................................
				If ln_Indx.Equals(-1)
					If Me.ct_FavList.Count >= Me.cn_Capacity
						Me.ct_FavList.RemoveAt(Me.ct_FavList.Count-1)
					End If
				Else
					Me.ct_FavList.RemoveAt(ln_Indx)
				End If
				'..................................................
				Dim lt_Cont								= New	SortedList(Of	Integer, SAPFavoriteDTO)(Me.cn_Capacity)
				Dim ln_Index	As Integer	= 1

				lt_Cont.Add(1, dataEntry)
				
				For Each	lo	In Me.ct_FavList

					ln_Index	+= 1
					lo.Value.SeqNo	= ln_Index
					lt_Cont.Add(ln_Index, lo.Value)

				Next
				'..................................................
				Me.ct_FavList	= lt_Cont

			End Sub

		#End Region
		'¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
		#Region "Constructor"

			'¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨
			Public Sub	New()

				Me.cn_Capacity	= 5
				Me.CreateList()

			End Sub

		#End Region
		'¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
		#Region "Methods: Private"

			'¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨
			Private	Sub	ResizeList()

				Dim	lt_List	=	New	SortedList(Of	Integer, SAPFavoriteDTO)(Me.cn_Capacity)

				For Each lo In Me.ct_FavList

					lt_List.Add(lo.Key,lo.Value)
					If lt_List.Count >= Me.cn_Capacity
						Exit For
					End If

				Next

				Me.ct_FavList	= lt_List

			End Sub
			'¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨
			Private	Function	CheckExists(ByVal DTO	As SAPFavoriteDTO)	As Integer

				Dim ln_Ret	As Integer = -1

				For Each	lo	In Me.ct_FavList

					If	lo.Value.Client.Equals(	DTO.Client)	AndAlso
							lo.Value.ID.Equals(DTO.ID)

						ln_Ret	=	Me.ct_FavList.IndexOfKey(lo.Key)
						Exit	For

					End If

				Next

				Return	ln_Ret

			End Function
			'¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨¨
			Private Sub CreateList()

				Me.ct_FavList	=	New	SortedList(Of	Integer, SAPFavoriteDTO)(Me.cn_Capacity)

			End Sub

		#End Region

	End Class

